headlines.description: — After starting 1-4, things looked bleak for the Miami Heat. Now that stretch seems almost forgotten.
headlines.shortLinkText: Butler scores 36, Robinson adds 26 and Heat top Nets 122-115 to win 7th straight

events.name: Oklahoma City Thunder at Golden State Warriors

headlines.description: — Even after making nearly 60% of their 3-pointers, the Oklahoma City Thunder were just as pleased with how they moved the ball around the court in recording 31 assists.
headlines.shortLinkText: Isaiah Joe goes 7 for 7 on 3-pointers, Thunder send short-handed Warriors to fifth straight loss
